These calligraphic elements exhibit the physical truth of woodblock printing: subtle embossment, ink‑squeeze at stroke terminations, and visible paper fibre. The vermilion stamps are matte and slightly chalky.

8. CARTOGRAPHIC DETAILS — COMPASS ROSE, SCALE, & MARGINALIA
